  "text": "Absorb BVS is composed of polymer backbone of poly l-lactic acid (PLLA), coated with a layer of a 1:1 mixture of poly d, l-lactic acid (PDLLA) eluting an anti-proliferative drug, everolimus (100 µ/cm 2 ). Polymer tubes are extruded into thick-walled, small diameter tubes followed by laser cutting [CITATION_1] . Absorb BVS has 157 µm strut thickness and design of in-phase zig-zag hoops linked with bridges ( Fig. 1) .",
